<td data-valign="top"><p><span id="img_01200"></span> <img src="img/01200.jpg" alt="D" /></p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>DHE, eisd ri m’ urnuigh,<br />
Lub rium do chluas,<br />
Leig m’ achan agus m’ urnuigh.<br />
T' ionnsuidh a suas.<br />
Thig, a Righ na glorach<br />
Da m’ chomhnadh a nuas,<br />
A Righ na bith ’s na trocair,<br />
Le comhnadh an Uain,<br />
A Mhic na Muire Oighe<br />
Da m’ chomhnadh le buadh,<br />
A Mhic na Muire mine<br />
Is finne-ghile snuadh.</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>GOD, listen to my prayer,<br />
Bend to me Thine ear,<br />
Let my supplications and my prayers<br />
Ascend to Thee upwards,<br />
Come, Thou King of Glory,<br />
To protect me down,<br />
Thou King of life and mercy<br />
With the aid of the Lamb.<br />
Thou Son of Mary Virgin<br />
To protect me with power,<br />
Thou Son of the lovely Mary<br />
Of purest fairest beauty.</p></td>
</tr>
